comments: Johnson (SAS) makes contact with DeRozan?s (CHI) right wrist prior to release, which affects his jump shot attempt.
Poeltl (SAS) establishes himself in Dragic?s (CHI) path and absorbs contact to his side during the pick.
McDermott (SAS) brushes Green's (CHI) right arm during the fast-break, and marginal contact occurs.
Drummond (CHI) and Poeltl (SAS) engage and disengage off-ball as they attempt to establish post position, and marginal contact occurs.
Caruso (CHI) and Richardson (SAS) move off-ball around the screen , and Richardson momentarily loses his balance before going to the ground.
Drummond (CHI) reaches towards the pass, and incidental foot-to-foot contact with Poeltl (SAS) results in him losing his balance.
Green (CHI) legally saves the ball in-bounds.
Jones (SAS) releases the shot attempt prior to the shot clock expiring.
Green (CHI) moves into Jones' (SAS) path during his drive but the contact is marginal.
Caruso (CHI) attempts to commit a take foul on Jones (SAS).
Dragic (CHI) initiates contact with Jones? (SAS) left arm, which affects his upward shooting motion on the driving shot attempt.
White's (CHI) right leg naturally drifts forward following the release of his jump shot attempt, and Sochan (SAS) initiates lower body contact that affects White's ability to follow-through.
Sochan (SAS) calls and is rewarded a timeout prior to exhausting five seconds from his inbound opportunity.
White (CHI) commits a take foul on Johnson (SAS).
